o the House"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of God, at Mekkeh"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (T, S;) because people repair to it every year. (T, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haj~uwA mak~apa", "text_ar": "حَجُّوا مَكَّةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They performed the pilgrimage to Mekkeh"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA Haj~a wal`kin~ahu daj~a", "text_ar": "مَا حَجَّ وَلٰكِنَّهُ دَجَّ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He did not repair to Mekkeh to visit the House of God,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Tálib, Az,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for the performance of the rites and ceremonies of the pilgrimage,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "but he journeyed for mercantile purposes."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Tálib, Az, Msb. [See also art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "dj", "text_ar": "دج"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]) And hence, accord. to some,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laj~a faHaj~a", "text_ar": "لَجَّ فَحَجَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", a prov., which see below. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, (TA,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haj~N", "text_ar": "حَجٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He came,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "arrived."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haj~a EalayonaA fulaAnN", "text_ar": "حَجَّ عَلَيْنَا فُلَانٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one came to us."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)       -A2-  Also, [aor., accord. to rule, as above,] inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haj~N", "text_ar": "حَجٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He shaved"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[his head; as one does on completing the performance of the rites and ceremonies of the pilgrimage: 